    {
        "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820626",
        "quote": "In 1993, my first documentary was about the civil war in Algeria. That was in French and in Arabic. Another short film I did was silent. What I'm trying to say is that, yes, I'm Italian, and yes, I make films with Italian money, but personally, I've always been invested in the broader world of film-making.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Luca Guadagnino",
            "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820626"
        },
        "topics": [
