    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820627",
        "quote": "I have a number of projects that I've been dreaming of making ever since I was a child. But I am also very open to the chances of life and the chances of my profession.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Luca Guadagnino",
            "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820627"
