    {
        "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820606",
        "quote": "I'm a very eclectic person, and I enjoy multiple tastes; I'm like a bee who jumps from flower to flower. Before I die, I have to make a war movie, a Western, and a movie like Mike Nichols, because I love him.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Luca Guadagnino",
            "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820606"
