    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820600",
        "quote": "I personally don't think that blood ties should be something that signifies so much more than anything else. I understand perfectly when somebody leaves their family for good.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Luca Guadagnino",
