    {
        "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820614",
        "quote": "I am a film director, and I work with a visual language, with a visual medium. And I try to make virtue of the use of this visual medium. And I try to make sure what I do speaks the language of cinema.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Luca Guadagnino",
            "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820614"
        },
        "topics": [
