    {
        "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820623",
        "quote": "The concept of muse is alien to me. To speak of a muse implies there is a couple in which one person is the objectified passive element - there to help the creative, active, often male part of the duo to create. A muse is very passive. Who wants a muse? I don't want a muse.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Luca Guadagnino",
            "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820623"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Very",
