    {
        "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820628",
        "quote": "I grew up with a concept of cinema as a directorial thing, meaning the director is allowed to sail the ship. Not a dictatorial thing.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Luca Guadagnino",
            "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820628"
