    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820631",
        "quote": "I need to have a great deal of control and the ability to share my control with my collaborators and grant them the freedom and the quality of work I think these people deserve. If I don't have those elements, I walk away.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Luca Guadagnino",
            "url": "/quotes/luca_guadagnino_820631"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Deal",
